review_blob: One of the Best Crafts Ive tasted in a very long time. Not as ready available in the Local Bars as I think it could be. Better distribution *& this beer Lights up the CITY BEER SCENE !!

Great Pumpkin Ale. The Pumpkin Ale market has become saturated with beers that basically all last the same. At least the Pumpkin Ale has a distinctive Taste. I just wis it was more available in the NYC beer scene / bars.
